OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,FA police officer involved in the Henry
OL,7,FNowak case has resigned as Hampshire's
OL,8,FPolice and Crime Commissioner calls
OL,9,Ffor an "urgent inspection" to be
OL,10,Fcarried out into Hampshire and Isle of
OL,11,FWight Constabulary.
OL,13,FThe 18-year-old was murdered in
OL,14,FSouthampton in December by Vickrum
OL,15,FDigwa, 23, who stabbed the finance
OL,16,Fstudent five times with a 21cm blade
OL,17,Fthat he said he carried as part of his
OL,18,FSikh faith.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,FBody-worn camera footage from the
OL,7,Fincident appeared to show Mr Nowak,
OL,8,Fwho had received two stab wounds on
OL,9,Fthe back of his legs and a fatal wound
OL,10,Fto his heart, repeatedly pleading
OL,11,F"I've been stabbed" and "I can't
OL,12,Fbreathe" while being handcuffed by
OL,13,Fpolice.
OL,15,FHampshire Police said three of the
OL,16,Fofficers are still serving and one
OL,17,Fofficer has resigned.
OL,19,FIn a statement, they said they are all
OL,20,Fbeing treated as witnesses, so not
OL,21,Fsubject to any current restrictions.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@SO]sD@YOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,FPCC Donna Jones has written to the
OL,7,FInterim Chief Inspector of
OL,8,FConstabulary at His Majesty's
OL,9,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,10,Fand Rescue Services commissioning an
OL,11,Finspection into the police force.
OL,13,FIn the letter, she said: "This week,
OL,14,FVickrum Digwa was sentenced to life
OL,15,Fimprisonment with a minimum term of 21
OL,16,Fyears for Henry's murder.
OL,18,F"Henry Nowak was eighteen years old.
OL,19,FHe was a university student, a young
OL,20,Fman with his entire life ahead of him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,F"He died on a street in Southampton,
OL,7,Fhandcuffed, having told police
OL,8,Fofficers on multiple occasions that he
OL,9,Fhad been stabbed and that he could not
OL,10,Fbreathe.
OL,12,F"He was not believed. He was not
OL,13,Ftreated as a victim. He died while his
OL,14,Fkiller stood beside him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,F"I have described Henry's death
OL,7,Fpublicly as a national tragedy. The
OL,8,Fmanner in which Henry lost his life `
OL,9,Ffalsely accused by his attacker as he
OL,10,Flay dying, arrested, restrained, and
OL,11,Fdenied the immediate medical care he
OL,12,Fdesperately needed ` has rightly
OL,13,Fcaused profound public shock and
OL,14,Foutrage.
OL,16,F"The release of body-worn footage,
OL,17,Fwith the consent of Henry's family,
OL,18,Fhas brought that reality into sharp
OL,19,Fand devastating focus for the entire
OL,20,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,F"The public have seen what happened.
OL,7,FThey have heard Henry say "I can't
OL,8,Fbreathe". They deserve answers.
OL,10,F"Henry's family deserves answers."
OL,12,FShe continued: "The Independent Office
OL,13,Ffor Police Conduct is conducting an
OL,14,Finvestigation into the conduct of the
OL,15,Fofficers present at the scene, and I
OL,16,Fam committed to ensuring its findings
OL,17,Fare implemented without delay.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,F"However, I am satisfied that the
OL,7,Fcircumstances of Henry's death raise
OL,8,Fsystemic questions that go beyond
OL,9,Findividual officer conduct and which
OL,10,Fdemand independent scrutiny at the
OL,11,Finstitutional level."
OL,13,FPCC Donna Jones has asked the
OL,14,Finspection to address the culture and
OL,15,Fperformance of Hampshire and Isle of
OL,16,FWight Constabulary's Force Control
OL,17,FRoom.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,FThe letter said: "The body-worn
OL,7,Ffootage and the evidence heard during
OL,8,Fthe murder trial raise serious and
OL,9,Ftroubling questions about the
OL,10,Fintelligence available to officers
OL,11,Fbefore they arrived at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,F"Prior to their arrival, information
OL,7,Fexisted that pointed to a potential
OL,8,Fstabbing having taken place. The
OL,9,Finspection should examine: What
OL,10,Finformation was available to the force
OL,11,Fcontrol room regarding a potential
OL,12,Fstabbing before officers were
OL,13,Fdispatched to the scene, and whether
OL,14,Fthat information was communicated to
OL,15,Fresponding officers in full and in
OL,16,Ftime."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,FShe said the inspection should also
OL,7,Fexamine the training provided to
OL,8,Ffrontline officers on responding to
OL,9,Fstabbing incidents including the
OL,10,Frecognition of concealed injuries and
OL,11,Fserious internal bleeding which may
OL,12,Fnot be immediately visible.
OL,14,F"This inspection must be full and
OL,15,Ffrank," Donna Jones said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780481194
OL,3,CPCC calls for 'urgent inspection' into
OL,4,Cpolice after Henry Nowak's death
OL,6,F"It must be willing to identify not
OL,7,Fmerely individual errors but the
OL,8,Finstitutional conditions that made
OL,9,Fthose errors possible - in the control
OL,10,Froom, in training environments, and in
OL,11,Fthe culture of the force.
OL,13,F"It must make recommendations that are
OL,14,Fcapable of changing practice, both in
OL,15,FHampshire and in policing across
OL,16,Fcountry. No other family should have
OL,17,Fendure what Henry Nowak's family have
OL,18,Fendured."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
